  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a fast-paced retro arcade adventure with <strong>Eggbert</strong>, a daring red bird on a mission! In this classic-style platformer your goal is simple—but far from easy:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥚 <strong>Collect eggs</strong> that randomly appear across the level.<br>🦊 <strong>Avoid the cunning foxes</strong> that get faster and more relentless over time.<br>🐣 <strong>Hold onto the eggs</strong> until they hatch to earn points and climb the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With pixel-perfect platforming, increasing difficulty, and that addictive \"just one more try\" feel, Eggbert delivers the perfect blend of nostalgia and challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you outsmart the foxes and become the ultimate egg-hatching champion?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a fast-paced retro arcade adventure with <strong>Eggbert</strong>, a daring red bird on a mission! In this classic-style platformer your goal is simple—but far from easy:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥚 <strong>Collect eggs</strong> that randomly appear across the level.<br>🦊 <strong>Avoid the cunning foxes</strong> that get faster and more relentless over time.<br>🐣 <strong>Hold onto the eggs</strong> until they hatch to earn points and climb the leaderboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With pixel-perfect platforming, increasing difficulty, and that addictive \"just one more try\" feel, Eggbert delivers the perfect blend of nostalgia and challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you outsmart the foxes and become the ultimate egg-hatching champion?</p>",
